    <text>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_6a9b7b41">
            <lb />Rhythmic beat of a Gaucho dance<lb />-when Phanom Fingers play</div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_d7c2159d">
            <lb />These are the
            <seg ana="#phantom_body" resp="#np" type="topic">
                Phantom<lb />Hands
            </seg> of
            <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">
                a thousand
                <lb />immortal pianists; their
                <lb />glorious genius preserv-
                <lb />ed forever
            </seg>,
            <seg ana="#miracle" resp="#np" type="topic">
                through the<lb />miracle of Welte-<lb />Mignon*
                reproduction.
            </seg>
        </div>
            <div facs="#eSc_textblock_4cbe38c0">
            <lb />Wild abandon of a peasant
            <lb />song; lure of a Venetian love-
            <lb />lyric; simple charm of a plantation
            <lb />melody - who but the world's
            <lb />greatest masters can interpret these
            <lb />as a true music-lover demands?
            <lb />Why should you accept less when
            <lb />you can have a Welte-Mignon?
            <lb />Why should you be satisfied with
            <lb />any but the greatest of reproducing
            <lb />instruments with its hundrends of
            <lb />world-famous pianists?
            <lb />What a Christmas gift! The
        </div>
        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_bca02c58">
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#phantom_body" resp="#np" type="topic">
                phantom fingers
            </seg>
            of
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/118986724">Paderewski</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/116014490">De<lb />Pachmann</persName>,
            <persName corresp="https://d-nb.info/gnd/11918625X">Hofmann</persName>,
            <persName>Gabrilowitsch</persName>,
            <lb />and scores of others -
            <lb />
            <seg ana="#home" resp="#np" type="topic">
                playing in your own home
            </seg>
            <seg ana="#touch_of_a_button" resp="#np" type="topic">
                whenever you wish.
            </seg>
            <lb />See the
            Welte-Mignon* today.
            <seg ana="#invisibility" resp="#np" type="topic">
                It
                <lb />is invisible
            </seg>
            and does not interfere
            <lb />with manual playing. It is obtain-
            <lb />able in practically every good make
            <lb />of piano, both grand and upright.
            <lb />Write for interesting brochure,
            <lb /><orgName>Auto-Pneumatic Action Co.</orgName>
            <persName>W. C.
            <lb />Heaton</persName>, President, <address>12th Avenue at
            <lb />51st Street, New York.</address>
        </div>

        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_80ba3e2b">
